PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780927877
OL,3,CHow innocent man was jailed and the
OL,4,Creal rapist went free
OL,6,FA witness identifies Mr Malkinson at
OL,7,Fan identity parade.
OL,9,FA second witness picks a different
OL,10,Fmale, but then changes her mind and
OL,11,Fpicks out Mr Malkinson.
OL,13,FThey had both travelled to the parade
OL,14,Fin the same police car.
OL,16,FFebruary/March 2004
OL,18,FMr Malkinson is convicted and
OL,19,Fsentenced to life imprisonment with a
OL,20,Fminimum term of seven years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
