PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780927877
OL,3,CHow innocent man was jailed and the
OL,4,Creal rapist went free
OL,6,FA DNA profile is recovered from the
OL,7,Fvest top worn by the victim. It ruled
OL,8,Fout Mr Malkinson but identified a
OL,9,Fprofile from another man, "Unknown
OL,10,FMale 1", which "ought to have set
OL,11,Falarm bells ringing", Quinn's trial
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FMr Malkinson becomes eligible for
OL,15,Fparole but remains in jail because he
OL,16,Fis maintaining his innocence.
OL,18,FFebruary 2012
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780927877
OL,3,CHow innocent man was jailed and the
OL,4,Creal rapist went free
OL,6,FThe Criminal Cases Review Commission
OL,7,F(CCRC) refuses Mr Malkinson's
OL,8,Fapplication to refer his case back to
OL,9,Fthe Court of Appeal, dismissing the
OL,10,Fsignificance of the new DNA evidence.
OL,12,F13 December 2012
OL,14,FPolice take a DNA swab from Quinn -
OL,15,Fwho had been convicted of having sex
OL,16,Fwith a 12-year-old girl in 1992 - as
OL,17,Fpart of an operation to harvest DNA
OL,18,Fprofiles of known sex offenders.
OL,20,FFrom this point his DNA profile was
OL,21,Fnow on the national database.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780927877
OL,3,CHow innocent man was jailed and the
OL,4,Creal rapist went free
OL,6,F27 February 2020
OL,8,FCCRC decide not to refer Mr
OL,9,FMalkinson's application to the Court
OL,10,Fof Appeal for the second time.
OL,12,FThe Henley review found if analysis of
OL,13,Fthe "Unknown Male 1" DNA sample had
OL,14,Fbeen carried out, a potential match to
OL,15,FQuinn would have been made.
OL,17,FDecember 2020
OL,19,FMr Malkinson is released from prison
OL,20,Fon licence, having served more than 17
OL,21,Fyears
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
