FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780927877
OL,3,CHow innocent man was jailed and the
OL,4,Creal rapist went free
OL,6,FOctober 2022
OL,8,FA check on the police database showed
OL,9,Fa one in a billion profile match
OL,10,Fbetween the DNA sample from the rape
OL,11,Fvictim's vest top and sex offender
OL,12,FPaul Quinn - now living in Devon - but
OL,13,Fat the time living just a mile from
OL,14,Fthe crime scene.
OL,16,F13 December 2022
OL,18,FQuinn is arrested for rape and denies
OL,19,Fany involvement.
OL,21,F26 July 2023
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
