CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780927877
OL,3,CHow innocent man was jailed and the
OL,4,Creal rapist went free
OL,6,FMr Malkinson's conviction is quashed
OL,7,Fby the Court of Appeal.
OL,9,FHe says "the system" had let him and
OL,10,Fthe victim down, accusing the police
OL,11,Fof a "cover up". Greater Manchester
OL,12,FPolice apologises to him.
OL,14,FQuinn is convicted of rape, nearly 23
OL,15,Fyears after the attack.
OL,17,FManchester Crown Court heard he had
OL,18,Fsearched online to see how long police
OL,19,Fkept DNA samples.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780927877
OL,3,CHow innocent man was jailed and the
OL,4,Creal rapist went free
OL,6,FIt also heard that, in 2019, Quinn
OL,7,Fvisited an article about Mr
OL,8,FMalkinson's conviction - then moments
OL,9,Flater - searched "wrongful convictions
OL,10,Fuk".
OL,12,FQuinn is jailed for 21 years with an
OL,13,Fextended licence period of three
OL,14,Fyears, as Mr Justice Robert Bright
OL,15,Ftells him: "You sat back and enjoyed
OL,16,Fyour liberty at the expense of an
OL,17,Finnocent man."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
